National Grid plc - Wikipedia






















 






National Grid plc

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the energy company. For the electric power transmission network, see National Grid (Great Britain).

National Grid plc





Type

Public limited company


Traded as



LSE: NG
NYSE: NGG
FTSE 100 Component





